data.description: Nice remodeled 2BR 2.5 Bath Townhome near LSU Bus Line. This home features vinyl wood flooring downstairs, granite countertops, like-new appliances, carpet on stairs and in the two bedrooms, and an upstairs laundry convenient to the bedrooms. Both bedrooms have their own en-suite bath and large walk-in closet.  The refrigerator and washer/dryer will remain with the unit. This home is great for first-time homebuyers or an Investor. The rents Range from $900-$1200 per mth and the neighborhood is pet friendly with plenty of green space and pet stations. Book your showing today!!
